Merhaba! İsteğinizi anladım. Belirtilen SPEC-v1.txt dosyasına göre minigit     
aracını C dilinde uygulayacağım. Derleme için bir Makefile ve aracın kendisi   
için minigit.c dosyalarını oluşturacağım. Uygulama, test-v1.sh betiğindeki tüm 
testleri geçecek şekilde tasarlanacaktır.                                      

İşte istenen değişiklikler ve yeni dosyalar:                                   

1. Değişikliklerin Açıklaması                                                  

 • Makefile: C kodunu derleyip minigit adında çalıştırılabilir bir dosya       
   oluşturmak için yeni bir Makefile eklenecektir. Bu dosya, make komutuyla    
   projenin kolayca derlenmesini sağlar.                                       
 • minigit.c: SPEC-v1.txt'de belirtilen init, add, commit ve log komutlarının  
   tüm mantığını içeren yeni bir C kaynak dosyası oluşturulacaktır. Bu dosya,  
   belirtilen özel hash algoritmasını (MiniHash) uygulayacak ve tüm dosya      
   sistemi işlemlerini yönetecektir.                                           

2. Dosya Çıktıları                                                             

Aşağıda istenen Makefile ve minigit.c dosyalarının tam içeriği bulunmaktadır.  

Makefile                                                                       

                                                                               
CC = gcc                                                                       
                                                                               
CFLAGS = -Wall -Wextra -std=c99 -O2                                            
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
all: minigit                                                                   
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
minigit: minigit.c                                                             
                                                                               
    $(CC) $(CFLAGS) -o minigit minigit.c                                       
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
clean:                                                                         
                                                                               
    rm -f minigit                                                              
                                                                               

minigit.c                                                                      

                                                                               
#include <stdio.h>                                                             
                                                                               
#include <stdlib.h>                                                            
                                                                               
#include <string.h>                                                            
                                                                               
#include <stdint.h>                                                            
                                                                               
#include <sys/stat.h>                                                          
                                                                               
#include <sys/types.h>                                                         
                                                                               
#include <unistd.h>                                                            
                                                                               
#include <time.h>                                                              
                                                                               
#include <limits.h>                                                            
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
#define MINIGIT_DIR ".minigit"                                                 
                                                                               
#define OBJECTS_DIR ".minigit/objects"                                         
                                                                               
#define COMMITS_DIR ".minigit/commits"                                         
                                                                               
#define INDEX_FILE ".minigit/index"                                            
                                                                               
#define HEAD_FILE ".minigit/HEAD"                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
char* minihash(const void* data, size_t size);                                 
                                                                               
void handle_init();                                                            
                                                                               
void handle_add(const char* filename);                                         
                                                                               
void handle_commit(const char* message);                                       
                                                                               
void handle_log();                                                             
                                                                               
void read_file_content(const char* path, char** buffer, size_t* size);         
                                                                               
void write_file_content(const char* path, const void* content, size_t size);   
                                                                               
int path_exists(const char* path);                                             
                                                                               
int compare_strings(const void* a, const void* b);                             
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
int main(int argc, char *argv[]) {                                             
                                                                               
    if (argc < 2) {                                                            
                                                                               
        return 1;                                                              
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    if (strcmp(argv[1], "init") == 0) {                                        
                                                                               
        if (argc != 2) return 1;                                               
                                                                               
        handle_init();                                                         
                                                                               
    } else if (strcmp(argv[1], "add") == 0) {                                  
                                                                               
        if (argc != 3) return 1;                                               
                                                                               
        handle_add(argv[2]);                                                   
                                                                               
    } else if (strcmp(argv[1], "commit") == 0) {                               
                                                                               
        if (argc != 4 || strcmp(argv[2], "-m") != 0) return 1;                 
                                                                               
        handle_commit(argv[3]);                                                
                                                                               
    } else if (strcmp(argv[1], "log") == 0) {                                  
                                                                               
        if (argc != 2) return 1;                                               
                                                                               
        handle_log();                                                          
                                                                               
    } else {                                                                   
                                                                               
        return 1;                                                              
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    return 0;                                                                  
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
char* minihash(const void* data, size_t size) {                                
                                                                               
    uint64_t h = 1469598103934665603ULL;                                       
                                                                               
    const unsigned char* p = (const unsigned char*)data;                       
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    for (size_t i = 0; i < size; ++i) {                                        
                                                                               
        h = h ^ p[i];                                                          
                                                                               
        h = h * 1099511628211ULL;                                              
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    char* hex_hash = (char*)malloc(17);                                        
                                                                               
    if (!hex_hash) {                                                           
                                                                               
        perror("malloc");                                                      
                                                                               
        exit(1);                                                               
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
    snprintf(hex_hash, 17, "%016lx", h);                                       
                                                                               
    return hex_hash;                                                           
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
void handle_init() {                                                           
                                                                               
    if (path_exists(MINIGIT_DIR)) {                                            
                                                                               
        printf("Repository already initialized\n");                            
                                                                               
        return;                                                                
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    mkdir(MINIGIT_DIR, 0755);                                                  
                                                                               
    mkdir(OBJECTS_DIR, 0755);                                                  
                                                                               
    mkdir(COMMITS_DIR, 0755);                                                  
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    FILE* index = fopen(INDEX_FILE, "w");                                      
                                                                               
    if (index) fclose(index);                                                  
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    FILE* head = fopen(HEAD_FILE, "w");                                        
                                                                               
    if (head) fclose(head);                                                    
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
void handle_add(const char* filename) {                                        
                                                                               
    if (!path_exists(filename)) {                                              
                                                                               
        printf("File not found\n");                                            
                                                                               
        exit(1);                                                               
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    char* content;                                                             
                                                                               
    size_t size;                                                               
                                                                               
    read_file_content(filename, &content, &size);                              
                                                                               
    if (content == NULL) {                                                     
                                                                               
        printf("File not found\n");                                            
                                                                               
        exit(1);                                                               
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    char* hash = minihash(content, size);                                      
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    char object_path[PATH_MAX];                                                
                                                                               
    snprintf(object_path, PATH_MAX, "%s/%s", OBJECTS_DIR, hash);               
                                                                               
    write_file_content(object_path, content, size);                            
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    free(content);                                                             
                                                                               
    free(hash);                                                                
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    FILE* index_f = fopen(INDEX_FILE, "r");                                    
                                                                               
    char line[PATH_MAX];                                                       
                                                                               
    int found = 0;                                                             
                                                                               
    if (index_f) {                                                             
                                                                               
        while (fgets(line, sizeof(line), index_f)) {                           
                                                                               
            line[strcspn(line, "\n")] = 0;                                     
                                                                               
            if (strcmp(line, filename) == 0) {                                 
                                                                               
                found = 1;                                                     
                                                                               
                break;                                                         
                                                                               
            }                                                                  
                                                                               
        }                                                                      
                                                                               
        fclose(index_f);                                                       
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    if (!found) {                                                              
                                                                               
        index_f = fopen(INDEX_FILE, "a");                                      
                                                                               
        if (!index_f) {                                                        
                                                                               
            perror("fopen");                                                   
                                                                               
            exit(1);                                                           
                                                                               
        }                                                                      
                                                                               
        fprintf(index_f, "%s\n", filename);                                    
                                                                               
        fclose(index_f);                                                       
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
void handle_commit(const char* message) {                                      
                                                                               
    struct stat st;                                                            
                                                                               
    if (stat(INDEX_FILE, &st) != 0 || st.st_size == 0) {                       
                                                                               
        printf("Nothing to commit\n");                                         
                                                                               
        exit(1);                                                               
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    char parent_hash[17];                                                      
                                                                               
    strcpy(parent_hash, "NONE");                                               
                                                                               
    FILE* head_f = fopen(HEAD_FILE, "r");                                      
                                                                               
    if (head_f) {                                                              
                                                                               
        if (fread(parent_hash, 1, 16, head_f) == 16) {                         
                                                                               
            parent_hash[16] = '\0';                                            
                                                                               
        } else {                                                               
                                                                               
            strcpy(parent_hash, "NONE");                                       
                                                                               
        }                                                                      
                                                                               
        fclose(head_f);                                                        
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    char** filenames = NULL;                                                   
                                                                               
    int file_count = 0;                                                        
                                                                               
    FILE* index_f = fopen(INDEX_FILE, "r");                                    
                                                                               
    char line[PATH_MAX];                                                       
                                                                               
    while (fgets(line, sizeof(line), index_f)) {                               
                                                                               
        line[strcspn(line, "\n")] = 0;                                         
                                                                               
        filenames = (char**)realloc(filenames, (file_count + 1) *              
sizeof(char*));                                                                
                                                                               
        filenames[file_count] = strdup(line);                                  
                                                                               
        file_count++;                                                          
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
    fclose(index_f);                                                           
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    qsort(filenames, file_count, sizeof(char*), compare_strings);              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    size_t content_len = 0;                                                    
                                                                               
    char* commit_content = NULL;                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    char buffer[4096];                                                         
                                                                               
    snprintf(buffer, sizeof(buffer), "parent: %s\n", parent_hash);             
                                                                               
    content_len += strlen(buffer);                                             
                                                                               
    commit_content = strdup(buffer);                                           
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    snprintf(buffer, sizeof(buffer), "timestamp: %ld\n", time(NULL));          
                                                                               
    content_len += strlen(buffer);                                             
                                                                               
    commit_content = (char*)realloc(commit_content, content_len + 1);          
                                                                               
    strcat(commit_content, buffer);                                            
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    snprintf(buffer, sizeof(buffer), "message: %s\n", message);                
                                                                               
    content_len += strlen(buffer);                                             
                                                                               
    commit_content = (char*)realloc(commit_content, content_len + 1);          
                                                                               
    strcat(commit_content, buffer);                                            
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    const char* files_header = "files:\n";                                     
                                                                               
    content_len += strlen(files_header);                                       
                                                                               
    commit_content = (char*)realloc(commit_content, content_len + 1);          
                                                                               
    strcat(commit_content, files_header);                                      
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    for (int i = 0; i < file_count; i++) {                                     
                                                                               
        char* file_content;                                                    
                                                                               
        size_t file_size;                                                      
                                                                               
        read_file_content(filenames[i], &file_content, &file_size);            
                                                                               
        char* blob_hash = minihash(file_content, file_size);                   
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
        snprintf(buffer, sizeof(buffer), "%s %s\n", filenames[i], blob_hash);  
                                                                               
        content_len += strlen(buffer);                                         
                                                                               
        commit_content = (char*)realloc(commit_content, content_len + 1);      
                                                                               
        strcat(commit_content, buffer);                                        
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
        free(file_content);                                                    
                                                                               
        free(blob_hash);                                                       
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    char* commit_hash = minihash(commit_content, content_len);                 
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    char commit_path[PATH_MAX];                                                
                                                                               
    snprintf(commit_path, PATH_MAX, "%s/%s", COMMITS_DIR, commit_hash);        
                                                                               
    write_file_content(commit_path, commit_content, content_len);              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    write_file_content(HEAD_FILE, commit_hash, strlen(commit_hash));           
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    fclose(fopen(INDEX_FILE, "w"));                                            
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    printf("Committed %s\n", commit_hash);                                     
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    free(commit_content);                                                      
                                                                               
    free(commit_hash);                                                         
                                                                               
    for (int i = 0; i < file_count; i++) {                                     
                                                                               
        free(filenames[i]);                                                    
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
    free(filenames);                                                           
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
void handle_log() {                                                            
                                                                               
    char current_hash[17];                                                     
                                                                               
    FILE* head_f = fopen(HEAD_FILE, "r");                                      
                                                                               
    if (!head_f || fread(current_hash, 1, 16, head_f) != 16) {                 
                                                                               
        printf("No commits\n");                                                
                                                                               
        if(head_f) fclose(head_f);                                             
                                                                               
        return;                                                                
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
    current_hash[16] = '\0';                                                   
                                                                               
    fclose(head_f);                                                            
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    while (strlen(current_hash) == 16 && strcmp(current_hash, "NONE") != 0) {  
                                                                               
        char commit_path[PATH_MAX];                                            
                                                                               
        snprintf(commit_path, PATH_MAX, "%s/%s", COMMITS_DIR, current_hash);   
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
        FILE* commit_f = fopen(commit_path, "r");                              
                                                                               
        if (!commit_f) break;                                                  
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
        char line[4096];                                                       
                                                                               
        char parent_hash[17] = "NONE";                                         
                                                                               
        long timestamp = 0;                                                    
                                                                               
        char message[4096] = "";                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
        while (fgets(line, sizeof(line), commit_f)) {                          
                                                                               
            char temp_parent[41];                                              
                                                                               
            if (sscanf(line, "parent: %40s", temp_parent) == 1) {              
                                                                               
                strncpy(parent_hash, temp_parent, 16);                         
                                                                               
                parent_hash[16] = '\0';                                        
                                                                               
            } else if (sscanf(line, "timestamp: %ld", &timestamp) == 1) {      
                                                                               
                // Parsed                                                      
                                                                               
            } else if (strncmp(line, "message: ", 9) == 0) {                   
                                                                               
                strcpy(message, line + 9);                                     
                                                                               
                message[strcspn(message, "\n")] = 0;                           
                                                                               
            } else if (strcmp(line, "files:\n") == 0) {                        
                                                                               
                break;                                                         
                                                                               
            }                                                                  
                                                                               
        }                                                                      
                                                                               
        fclose(commit_f);                                                      
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
        printf("commit %s\n", current_hash);                                   
                                                                               
        printf("Date: %ld\n", timestamp);                                      
                                                                               
        printf("Message: %s\n", message);                                      
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
        strcpy(current_hash, parent_hash);                                     
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
void read_file_content(const char* path, char** buffer, size_t* size) {        
                                                                               
    FILE* f = fopen(path, "rb");                                               
                                                                               
    if (!f) {                                                                  
                                                                               
        *buffer = NULL; *size = 0;                                             
                                                                               
        return;                                                                
                                                                               
    }                                                                          
                                                                               
    fseek(f, 0, SEEK_END);                                                     
                                                                               
    long fsize = ftell(f);                                                     
                                                                               
    fseek(f, 0, SEEK_SET);                                                     
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
    *buffer = (char*)malloc(fsize);                                            
                                                                               
    if (!*buffer) { fclose(f); perror("malloc"); exit(1); }                    
                                                                               
    *size = fread(*buffer, 1, fsize, f);                                       
                                                                               
    fclose(f);                                                                 
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
void write_file_content(const char* path, const void* content, size_t size) {  
                                                                               
    FILE* f = fopen(path, "wb");                                               
                                                                               
    if (!f) { perror("fopen"); exit(1); }                                      
                                                                               
    fwrite(content, 1, size, f);                                               
                                                                               
    fclose(f);                                                                 
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
int path_exists(const char* path) {                                            
                                                                               
    struct stat st;                                                            
                                                                               
    return stat(path, &st) == 0;                                               
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               
                                                                               
                                                                               
int compare_strings(const void* a, const void* b) {                            
                                                                               
    return strcmp(*(const char**)a, *(const char**)b);                         
                                                                               
}                                                                              
                                                                               

